## Tag component — while present on the Match, the table can be slapped
## (real-life WAR: everyone slaps the pile). Stamped when a WAR is decided,
## removed either by the slap itself (InputSystem) or when the pot sweep
## beat arrives (ResolveSystem._award). A fast click during the window
## snatches cards off the CPU's deck.
class_name C_SlapWindow
extends Component
